dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:4,660,000]. Dedicated to Major James Rennell, by A. Arrowsmith, January 1st 1801."Engraved by George Allen." Ornate title cartouche, with military regalia. Greenwich meridian. Relief shown pictorially with shading. Dimensions: 125 x 145 centimeters
